				<p class="text privacy_section_header">Contributing Writers</p>
					<li class="text terms_li_no_bullet">We are currently hiring contributing researchers and writers for the online platform to help break down legislation, write for our tumblr blog and identify trends in Westminster and in the media. It is essential that candidates display impeccable time management, as work is deadline driven. We require applicants to have outstanding academic records and the ability to write objective and engaging pieces.</li>

